        <h2 class="font-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-fg sm:text-3xl">Get in touch</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl leading-relaxed text-fg2">
          I'm open to backend and Spring Boot opportunities. Whether you have a question, a project,
          or just want to say hi — my inbox is always open.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
          <a
            href={`mailto:${email}`}
            class="w-full rounded-lg bg-accent px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-on-accent transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/25 sm:w-auto"
